  "title": "Cleared for a New Life",
  "summary": "Senior Agent Drax Rendolen visits the political prisoner Liora Kovani, a young defector ex-Imperial medic held in converted base housing on Ord Mantell, to conduct her clearance interview. Rather than interrogating her, the Alderaanian, himself a former Imperial, disarms her hostility with caf and frank talk, pressing her to say what she truly wants from her new life; she admits she wants to keep practicing medicine, the one thing she knows. Drawing on his own experience of defection and the example of the tough 'Ambassador' Delgard who restarted Liora's heart, Drax assures her she has family and purpose to lean on. He reveals the Jedi have cleared her of any lingering mental tampering, formally welcomes Liora Kovani to the New Republic, and sets her free, telling her to face the galaxy with an open mind.",
